data.eml:eml: A new species of Branchinecta (Crustacea: Branchiopoda: Anostraca) from the Argentinian Tierra del Fuego

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Cohen, Rosa Graciela (2008): A new species of Branchinecta (Crustacea: Branchiopoda: Anostraca) from the Argentinian Tierra del Fuego. Zootaxa 1884: 60-68, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.184274
